name: Channel Members Block in Channel Configuration page
objective: Channel Members Block in Channel Configuration page

customFields.Priority P1 to P4: P3 - Deep Functions (Do extensive scenarios work?)

inline.description:
1. Login to System Console as sysadmin user and visit Channel Page.
2. Click on any Channel which is not LDAP Group Synced.
3. Check the Members block is displayed and list of members in the Channel is correctly displayed.
inline.expectedResult: 3. Members block should be displayed in the Channel Configuration page and the list of members should be displayed correctly.
